Anthony Joshua: 'Medal represents my journey'
Team GB boxer Anthony Joshua has ensured a golden end to London 2012 with victory in his super-heavyweight bout on the final day of competition.He beat Italian Roberto Cammarelle to win GB's 29th gold medal of the Games.Speaking to BBC News, the boxer said ''That medal represents my journey. It's much more than a gold medal, it's a life experience.''